{
  "texts": [
    "For example, the publications of previous years starting from 2004 are in blue, the year 2012 are in green, the year 2017 are in yellow and the year 2023 are in red.",
    "From the plot, we deduce that in the year 2015-2022, notable key themes are question & answering system, software app developer, recommendation system, image processing, video features, events & scene, algorithms (neural topic models, plsa, dmm, multilingual topic model, acoustic topic model), model evaluation (human evaluation/judgement) and speech recognition.",
    "While, in 2023, notable key themes are literature review, policy implication, climate change, news, sentiment analysis (vader, anger, sadness), electronic health record, disease (diabetes, COVID-19 and vaccine) and mental health (schizophrenia and depression).",
    "Overall, these themes provide an indication on what the research documents are about.",
    "An analysis of co-occurrences identifies terms associated with each other and maps them according to their relatedness to closely monitor the relationship between documents."
  ]
}